<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/137576-why-did-this-horrible-book-get-the-nobel">Why did this horrible book get the Nobel Prize? It&#39;s ironical (a word used many times in the book).</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_137576'><a id="like_count_community_question_137576" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/137576?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">6 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F24100.The_Golden_Notebook">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/137576-why-did-this-horrible-book-get-the-nobel">7 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/137576-why-did-this-horrible-book-get-the-nobel">See all 5 answers</a>
</li>
